archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: SAR2 Application Cooperation
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This view shows high level application cooperation of components that realize the Security Architecture Review 2 (SAR2). For clarity we have left out some details around information flow which can be found in the view titled "SAR2 Information Flow"
This application solution serves the Security Architecture Review Service.
The SAR2 solution is a little more complex than SAR1 because it includes a review with the Enterprise Security Architecture team, which means there are some manual steps that need to be facilitated.
After the SAR User submits a self-assessed review, the Enterprise Security Architect and SAR2 Use then Review Together. The Enterprise Security Architect then Utilizes the SAR2 Review solution for quick editing of the review material, whilst the SAR User is busy providing evidence.
